Empathic Link			KEY:Mephit Underling ~ Empathic Link		SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Features.Mephit Underling Class Features.SpecialQuality		DESC:An Elemental Archon has an empathic link with their underlings out to a distance of one mile. The archon cannot see through the underlings' eyes, but each underling can communicate with the archon telepathically.
Improved Evasion		KEY:Mephit Underling ~ Improved Evasion		SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Features.Mephit Underling Class Features.SpecialQuality		DESC:If the underling is subjected to an attack that normally allows a Reflex save for half damage, it takes no damage on a successful save and only half damage on a failed save.
Shared Saving Throws		KEY:Mephit Underling ~ Shared Saving Throws	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Features.Mephit Underling Class Features.SpecialQuality		DESC:The underling uses its own base save or the Archon's whichever is better.
Sycophantic Fawning		KEY:Mephit Underling ~ Sycophantic Fawning	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Features.Mephit Underling Class Features.SpecialQuality		DESC:Underlings of experienced Archons are pleased to serve such paragons of perfection and they're more than happy to tell their master about how much they appreciate the privilege. Once per day as a standard action, a mephit underling may extol the virtues of its master, granting the Archon a +1 morale bonus on attack, damage, saves, and skill checks. The efforts of multiple underlings stack, lasting 1 round per HD of the highest HD mephit engaged in the fawning.
Improved Empathic Link		KEY:Mephit Underling ~ Improved Empathic Link	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Features.Mephit Underling Class Features.SpecialQuality		DESC:The empathic link extends to 20 miles.
Slavish Sacrifice		KEY:Mephit Underling ~ Slavish Sacrifice	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Features.Mephit Underling Class Features.SpecialQuality		DESC:The mephit underlings bond with its master is so great that it is willing to sacrifice itself for the Archon's wellbeing. Each morning, in a ceremony that takes 15 minutes, the Archon strengthens their link. For the entire day, the damage from a single attack that does damage enough that would bring the Archon below zero is transfer instantly to the nearest underling. Regardless of the amount of damage transferred the underling always dies, exploding in a sickening pop of elemental goo. An underling must be within 100 feet of the Archon for this to work.


