Moon's Hand			KEY:Silverstar ~ Moon's Hand			CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Silverstar Class Feature.SpecialQuality				SOURCEPAGE:p.202		DESC:Any heavy mace wielded by you is treated as if it were a +1 shock heavy mace. If it leaves your hand it reverts to its original abilities. If the weapon has additional abilities (such as frost), these abilities still apply, and if the weapon has an enhancement bonus better than +1 the higher of the two bonuses is used. At 6th level, the weapon is treated as a +2 shock heavy mace.
Tears of Selune			KEY:Silverstar ~ Tears of Selune			CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Class Feature.Silverstar Class Feature.SpecialQuality				SOURCEPAGE:p.202		DESC:You can project small balls of luminescent lunar energy from your eyes as a dancing lights spell (torches or will-o'-wisps only) at will, as if cast by a sorcerer of your caster level.
Prophet's Sight			KEY:Silverstar ~ Prophet's Sight			CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Silverstar Class Feature.SpecialQuality				SOURCEPAGE:p.202		DESC:Once per day, you are able to see as if under the effect of a true seeing spell cast by a cleric of your level. At 8th level, this ability can be used 2/day.
Selunite Lycanthrope			KEY:Silverstar ~ Selunite Lycanthrope			CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Class Feature.Silverstar Class Feature.SpecialQuality				SOURCEPAGE:p.202		DESC:If you contract any form of lycanthropy, you are treated as a natural lycanthrope. Your type changes to shapechanger, and you may select the Improved Control Shape feat (see the Monster Manual) or the Scent ability as a feat (see the Monster Manual) at any point that you can select a new feat. You do not change alignment due to contracting lycanthropy and are aware of your actions while in animal or hybrid form.
Moonshield			KEY:Silverstar ~ Moonshield			CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Silverstar Class Feature.SpecialQuality				SOURCEPAGE:p.202		ASPECT:SaveBonus|+2 saving throw bonus against enchantment, illusion, and necromancy spells and effects, and spells and effects with the darkness descriptor.		DESC:You have learned how to better resist the magic of the Shadow Weave. You gain a +2 bonus on saves against enchantment, illusion, and necromancy spells and effects, and spells and effects with the darkness descriptor. This bonus applies whether or not the source is from the Weave or the Shadow Weave.
Greater Moon's Hand			KEY:Silverstar ~ Greater Moon's Hand			CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Silverstar Class Feature.SpecialQuality				SOURCEPAGE:p.202		DESC:When using your moon's hand ability, you treat your heavy mace as if it were a +2 shocking burst weapon.
Moonfire			KEY:Silverstar ~ Moonfire			CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Class Feature.Silverstar Class Feature.SpecialQuality				SOURCEPAGE:p.202		DESC:You can cast Moonfire 1/day as a spell-like ability.



